    &lt;CommentText&gt;The length of time it takes to get through on the phone is ridiculous. My shortest phone call took 38 mins - 30 of which were on hold. Another phone call took over 1hr to answer and when I got through the guy sounded surprised that I needed to reschedule an appointment. It was like he had never heard of the concept before. I had to check that I was through to the right section. Then I was put on hold again so he could log into the system. Why have untrained people answering the phones? Why not provide an online system for making appointments and bypass these inept people?
 This is the same number you provide to let you know if people are running late for an appointment. No one can wait 1hr to let you know they are running 5mins late for an appointment. Not good enough.                When I saw the nurse she was professional and knowledgeable.&lt;/CommentText&gt;
